            <screenshot>resources/screenshot-13.jpg</screenshot>
            <screenshot>resources/screenshot-14.jpg</screenshot>
            <screenshot>resources/screenshot-15.jpg</screenshot>
		</assets>
        <news>
    v1.0.2
    - drobné úpravy (screenshots,ikony)

    v1.0.1(18.05.2020)
